cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with video processing and deep neural networks for location detection, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of resource-constrained smart cameras also suggests a focus on efficient algorithms and hardware implementation, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
